        {
            "id": 6435985,
            "title": "AI成長疑慮壓抑科技股那斯達克創一個月最大跌幅",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><img alt=\"Reuters/TPG\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6435985/o/c123d21ddc1d14de3f0e036fea7ab23c.jpg\"/></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"126\" data-start=\"26\">2026年04月29日（優分析／產業數據中心報導）⸺ 美股周二收低，投資人趕在大型科技股財報公布前轉趨謹慎，加上OpenAI成長疑慮再度升溫，拖累科技股與半導體族群走弱，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克</a>指數創一個月來最大單日跌幅。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section><p data-end=\"206\" data-start=\"128\">終場，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊工業指數</a>下跌0.05%至49,141.93點；標普500指數下跌0.49%至7,138.80點；<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克</a>指數下跌0.90%至24,663.80點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"319\" data-start=\"208\">市場焦點集中在AI投資熱潮能否延續。據報導，OpenAI近月每周用戶與營收未達內部目標，引發投資人擔心其是否有能力支撐龐大的資料中心支出。Oracle(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ORCL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ORCL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ORCL-US</a>)因雲端業務高度仰賴OpenAI題材，股價下跌4.1%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"464\" data-start=\"321\">半導體股同步承壓。Nvidia(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>)、AMD(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMD-US</a>)與Broadcom(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AVGO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AVGO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AVGO-US</a>)下跌1.6%至4.4%，Nvidia投資的CoreWeave(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRWV:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRWV\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRWV-US</a>)下跌5.8%。半導體族群今年以來累計漲幅已超過40%，在AI疑慮升溫下，部分投資人選擇先行獲利了結。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"639\" data-start=\"466\">本周財報進入高峰，Alphabet(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GOOGL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOGL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GOOGL-US</a>)、Amazon(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMZN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>)、Meta Platforms(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:META:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/META\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">META-US</a>)與Microsoft(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MSFT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MSFT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MSFT-US</a>)將於周三公布財報，Apple(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AAPL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AAPL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AAPL-US</a>)則於周四登場。Raymond James指出，本周公布財報的企業合計約占標普500總市值44%，財報結果將成為市場短線方向關鍵。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"800\" data-start=\"641\">個股方面，General Motors(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GM-US</a>)因季度利潤優於預期並上調全年獲利展望，股價上漲1.3%；United Parcel Service(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UPS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UPS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UPS-US</a>)雖維持全年營收目標，但燃料成本上升抵銷業務改善效益，股價下跌4.0%；Coca-Cola(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:KO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/KO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">KO-US</a>)財報優於預期並上調全年獲利目標，股價上漲3.9%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"889\" data-start=\"802\">總體面上，聯準會已召開利率會議，市場普遍預期周三將維持利率不變。投資人關注主席鮑爾會後談話，尤其是能源價格上漲是否加劇通膨壓力，進而影響後續政策路徑。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"990\" data-start=\"891\">地緣政治與油價也加重市場壓力。美國總統川普表示，對伊朗最新和平提案感到不滿，因該提案可能延後核問題談判，削弱市場對衝突降溫的期待。同時，阿拉伯聯合大公國宣布退出OPEC，油價急漲，再度引發通膨疑慮。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>※ 本文經「優分析」授權轉載，原文出處:<a href=\"https://uanalyze.com.tw/articles/6791751318\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color:#A9A9A9\">原文連結</a>\n<br/>※ 免責聲明：文中所提的個股、基金、期貨商品內容僅供參考，並非投資建議，投資人應獨立判斷，審慎評估風險。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p></p></section></main>",
